dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is John Martinez. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Kathryn. How can I assist you today?
I'd like to file a new claim. There was an incident with my car.
Of course, Kathryn. I will need some information to proceed. Can you please provide me with your policy number?
My policy number is five three seven two six.
Thank you. And could you also confirm your date of birth for verification purposes?
My date of birth is zero two one one, nineteen ninety.
Great, thank you for providing that information, Kathryn. I will start the new claim process now. Is there anything else you'd like to add before we proceed further?
No, that's all for now. Thank you for your help, John.
You're welcome, Kathryn. If you have any more questions, don't hesitate to reach out. Have a great day!
